      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this collector-grade masterpiece. Finished in a flawless deep metallic gloss that looks like liquid glass, this vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The interior remains in true showroom state, featuring supple, unscuffed premium leather that still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every body panel alignment is factory-precise, and the undercarriage is as pristine as the exterior finish. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from a new vehicle, delivering a tight, responsive drive backed by a complete, chronological service history. You will find no stone chips, no door dings, and zero bolster wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute pinnacle of quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
