      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It is honestly in flawless condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car smell. Not a single scratch or ding to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
